name: Cable-knit Sweater
description: Relaxed-fit sweater in soft, cable-knit fabric with wool content. Long, wide raglan sleeves and ribbing at neckline, cuffs, and hem. Polyester content is recycled.

name: Mom High Ankle Jeans
description: 5-pocket, ankle-length jeans in washed stretch cotton denim. Extra-high waist and straight legs. Slightly looser fit. Cotton content is partly recycled.

name: Stand-up-collar Puffer Jacket
description: Quilted, padded jacket in woven fabric. Stand-up collar, zipper at front with wind flap and concealed snap fasteners, and side pockets. Elasticized cuffs and hem. Lining and padding made from recycled polyester.

name: Embrace High Ankle Jeans
description: 5-pocket, ankle-length jeans in washed, stretch denim. High waist, zip fly with button, and super-skinny legs. Cotton content is partly recycled. Embrace – denim with smart stretch function that molds to body for a comfortable, flattering silhouette.

name: Balloon-sleeved Dress
description: Straight-cut, calf-length dress in airy, woven fabric. Small opening at back of neck with button, 3/4-length balloon sleeves with narrow elastic at cuffs, and slit at back of hem. Unlined.

name: Puff-sleeved Dress
description: Short dress in airy woven fabric. Small stand-up collar, V-shaped opening, and covered buttons at top. Gathered seam at waist and long, voluminous puff sleeves with button at cuffs. Lining in jersey made from recycled polyester.

name: Oversized Shirt Jacket
description: Oversized shirt jacket in woven fabric with soft, brushed inside. Collar, buttons at front, and yoke at back. Chest pockets with flap and button, diagonal side pockets, gently dropped shoulders, and long sleeves with button at cuffs. Short slits at sides and slightly longer hem at back. Unlined.

name: Hoodie
description: Wide-cut sweatshirt with a lined drawstring hood, kangaroo pocket, and ribbing at cuffs and hem.

name: Leggings with Creases
description: Leggings in stretch fabric. High waist and concealed, elasticized waistband. Stitched creases on legs and raw-edge hems.

name: Fluffy Sweater
description: Soft, fluffy, knit sweater with a round neckline, dropped shoulders, and long sleeves. Ribbing at neckline, cuffs, and hem.

name: Skinny Regular Ankle Jeans
description: Jeans in washed stretch denim with a regular waist and zip fly with button. Mock front pockets, regular back pockets, and skinny legs.

name: Tie Belt Coat
description: Coat in felted fabric with a low stand-up collar. Concealed buttons at front, discreet side-seam pockets, and a removable tie belt at waist. Lining in recycled polyester.

name: Tie Belt Coat
description: Coat in woven fabric with a soft, brushed finish. Notched lapels, wrapover front with concealed snap fasteners, and removable tie belt at waist. Discreet side pockets and vent at back. Satin lining. Polyester content of lining is partly recycled.

name: Faux Fur-lined Jacket
description: Straight-cut jacket with soft faux fur lining. Faux fur collar with adjustable tabs and metal buckles. Zipper at front, side pockets, and faux fur trim at cuffs and hem.

name: Slacks
description: Ankle-length slacks in woven, stretch fabric. Regular waist, concealed elasticized waistband, and zip fly with concealed hook-and-eye fastener. Side pockets, mock welt back pockets, and tapered legs.

name: Biker Jacket
description: Biker jacket in faux leather with a diagonal zipper at front. Notched lapels with decorative snap fasteners, side pockets with zipper, and zipper at cuffs. Tab at sides with decorative snap fastener. Lining in recycled polyester.

name: Double-breasted Jacket
description: Straight-cut, double-breasted jacket in woven fabric. Notched lapels, pearlescent buttons at front, and front pockets with flap. Gently tapered waist. Lined.

name: Cotton Leggings
description: Leggings in soft jersey made from an organic cotton blend. Wide, elasticized waistband.

name: Jacquard-weave Dress
description: Calf-length dress in jacquard-weave fabric. Round neckline and opening at back of neck with covered button. Short, wide raglan sleeves with narrow trim, seam at waist with drawstrings, and gathered tier on skirt for added volume. Jersey lining.

name: Wide-cut Cotton T-shirt
description: Wide-cut T-shirt in soft cotton jersey with a ribbed neckline.

name: Long Jacket
description: Longer jacket in woven fabric with notched lapels and welt front pockets with flap. Lined.

name: Jersey Turtleneck Top
description: Fitted turtleneck top in soft jersey with long sleeves.

name: Bouclé Skirt

name: MAMA Leggings

name: Pleated Skirt

name: Slim Fit Turtleneck Shirt

name: Jersey Shirt Jacket

name: Regular Fit Shirt Jacket

Regular Fit – classic fit with good room for movement and gently shaped waist for a comfortable, tailored silhouette.

name: Slim Fit Turtleneck Shirt
